---
import Card from '@/dashboard/components/ui/Card.astro'
---

<div id='match-failure'>
  <Card title='Fuera de Gamut' eyebrow='Resultado'>
    <button
      slot='right'
      type='button'
      data-action='reset'
      class='rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500'
    >
      Nueva igualación
    </button>

    <div class='rounded-lg border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 p-5' role='alert'>
      <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
        <svg
          xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
          viewBox='0 0 24 24'
          fill='none'
          stroke='currentColor'
          stroke-width='2'
          stroke-linecap='round'
          stroke-linejoin='round'
          class='mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600'
        >
          <path d='M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z'></path>
          <line x1='12' y1='9' x2='12' y2='13'></line>
          <line x1='12' y1='17' x2='12.01' y2='17'></line>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <div class='text-sm font-bold text-amber-900' data-message>
            El color objetivo cae fuera del gamut alcanzable con el inventario actual.
          </div>
          <div class='mt-1 text-xs text-amber-800'>
            Delta E <span class='font-bold' data-delta-e>—</span> excedió la tolerancia <span data-tolerance-label>—</span> (ΔE ≤ <span data-tolerance-value>—</span>). Amplía el inventario para alcanzar el espacio de color objetivo.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2'>
      <div>
        <div class='ch-label'>Color Objetivo</div>
        <div class='rounded-lg ring-1 ring-slate-200 overflow-hidden'>
          <div class='h-32' data-swatch-target style='background: rgb(180,180,180);'></div>
          <div class='flex justify-around bg-white px-2 py-2 text-[11px] tabular-nums text-slate-600'>
            <span>L <b class='text-slate-900' data-target-l>—</b></span>
            <span>a <b class='text-slate-900' data-target-a>—</b></span>
            <span>b <b class='text-slate-900' data-target-b>—</b></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class='ch-label'>Aproximación Más Cercana</div>
        <div class='rounded-lg ring-1 ring-slate-200 overflow-hidden'>
          <div class='h-32' data-swatch-closest style='background: rgb(180,180,180);'></div>
          <div class='flex justify-around bg-white px-2 py-2 text-[11px] tabular-nums text-slate-600'>
            <span>L <b class='text-slate-900' data-closest-l>—</b></span>
            <span>a <b class='text-slate-900' data-closest-a>—</b></span>
            <span>b <b class='text-slate-900' data-closest-b>—</b></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Closest recipe: the fórmula that produces the closest color even
        though it didn't meet the ΔE gate. In monopigmento formulation the
        model often can't match lightness exactly but the pigment RATIO is
        still directionally correct — surface it prominently so the operator
        can use it as a starting point and adjust total loading in planta. */}
    <div class='mt-5' data-closest-recipe-section hidden>
      <div class='mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-2'>
        <span class='inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-slate-700'>Orientativa</span>
        <div class='text-sm font-bold text-slate-800'>Fórmula Más Cercana</div>
      </div>
      <p class='mb-3 text-xs text-slate-500'>
        Aunque el color no se alcance exactamente, esta es la mezcla que <b>más se aproxima</b> con el inventario actual. El ratio entre pigmentos suele ser correcto — usa esta receta como punto de partida y ajusta la carga total en planta.
      </p>
      <div class='overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white'>
        <table class='min-w-full text-sm'>
          <thead class='bg-slate-50 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500'>
            <tr>
              <th class='px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold'>SKU</th>
              <th class='px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold'>Producto</th>
              <th class='px-4 py-2 text-right font-semibold'>% Carga</th>
              <th class='px-4 py-2 text-right font-semibold'>% del Blend</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody data-closest-recipe-body></tbody>
          <tfoot class='bg-slate-50/70 text-[11px] tabular-nums text-slate-600'>
            <tr>
              <td class='px-4 py-2' colspan='2'>Total pigmento</td>
              <td class='px-4 py-2 text-right font-bold text-slate-800' data-closest-recipe-total>—</td>
              <td class='px-4 py-2 text-right'>100%</td>
            </tr>
          </tfoot>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-5 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-5'>
      <div class='lg:col-span-3'>
        <div class='ch-label'>Plano de Cromaticidad a*/b*</div>
        <div class='rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4'>
          <svg viewBox='0 0 320 320' class='w-full' data-ab-plot>
            {/* Quadrant background: cyan/blue/green/yellow tint per CIELAB axis conventions */}
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id='ab-bg' x1='0' y1='0' x2='1' y2='1'>
                <stop offset='0%' stop-color='#fde68a' stop-opacity='0.35' />
                <stop offset='50%' stop-color='#fecaca' stop-opacity='0.35' />
                <stop offset='100%' stop-color='#bfdbfe' stop-opacity='0.35' />
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <rect x='20' y='20' width='280' height='280' fill='url(#ab-bg)' stroke='#e2e8f0' />
            {/* Grid */}
            <g stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='1'>
              <line x1='20' y1='160' x2='300' y2='160' />
              <line x1='160' y1='20' x2='160' y2='300' />
              <line x1='90' y1='20' x2='90' y2='300' stroke-dasharray='2 3' />
              <line x1='230' y1='20' x2='230' y2='300' stroke-dasharray='2 3' />
              <line x1='20' y1='90' x2='300' y2='90' stroke-dasharray='2 3' />
              <line x1='20' y1='230' x2='300' y2='230' stroke-dasharray='2 3' />
            </g>
            {/* Axis labels */}
            <g font-family='sans-serif' font-size='10' fill='#64748b'>
              <text x='306' y='163'>+a (rojo)</text>
              <text x='2' y='163'>−a</text>
              <text x='153' y='14'>−b</text>
              <text x='140' y='314'>+b (amarillo)</text>
              <text x='87' y='313' font-size='8'>−50</text>
              <text x='227' y='313' font-size='8'>+50</text>
              <text x='2' y='93' font-size='8'>−50</text>
              <text x='2' y='233' font-size='8'>+50</text>
            </g>
            {/* Line target → closest */}
            <line data-line stroke='#f97316' stroke-width='1.5' stroke-dasharray='4 3' x1='0' y1='0' x2='0' y2='0' />
            {/* Closest achievable */}
            <circle data-dot-closest cx='0' cy='0' r='6' fill='#10b981' stroke='#fff' stroke-width='2' />
            {/* Target */}
            <circle data-dot-target cx='0' cy='0' r='7' fill='#e11d48' stroke='#fff' stroke-width='2' />
          </svg>
          <div class='mt-3 flex justify-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-600'>
            <span class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <span class='inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-rose-600 ring-2 ring-white ring-offset-1 ring-offset-slate-200'></span>
              Objetivo
            </span>
            <span class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <span class='inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 ring-2 ring-white ring-offset-1 ring-offset-slate-200'></span>
              Aproximación más cercana
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='lg:col-span-2'>
        <div class='ch-label'>Cómo Cerrar la Brecha</div>
        <div class='rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-600'>
          <p>
            Agrega masterbatches en el
            <a class='font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:underline' href='/dashboard/calibration-lab'>Laboratorio de Calibración</a>
            que amplíen el gamut alcanzable alrededor del objetivo. Brechas comunes:
          </p>
          <ul class='mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5' data-gap-list>
            <li>Missing chromatic pigment along the hue axis of the target</li>
            <li>Insufficient tinting strength at 2.0% load</li>
            <li>Calibration curve inaccuracy — reshoot chips at 0.5/1.0/2.0%</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Primary: procurement targets — what pigments you'd need to buy */}
    <div class='mt-6' data-section-adquirir hidden>
      <div class='mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-2'>
        <span class='inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-amber-700'>Adquirir</span>
        <div class='text-sm font-bold text-slate-800'>Pigmentos que Necesitas para Alcanzar el Objetivo</div>
      </div>
      <p class='mb-2 text-xs text-slate-500'>
        Estos colores de referencia son los más cercanos al objetivo pero <b>no puedes producirlos con tu inventario actual</b>. Considera adquirir pigmentos capaces de alcanzarlos — con eso podrás igualar el color que pide el cliente.
      </p>
      <p class='mb-3 text-[11px] italic text-slate-400'>
        Sólo mostramos referencias con ΔE ≤ 20 al objetivo — por encima, están en otra familia de color y no ayudarían a alcanzarlo.
      </p>
      <div class='grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2' data-suggestions-adquirir></div>
    </div>

    {/* Secondary: reachable alternatives you could offer instead */}
    <div class='mt-6' data-section-alternativos hidden>
      <div class='mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-2'>
        <span class='inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-emerald-700'>Disponible</span>
        <div class='text-sm font-bold text-slate-800'>Colores Alternativos que Sí Puedes Producir</div>
      </div>
      <p class='mb-2 text-xs text-slate-500'>
        Si el cliente acepta un cambio, estos colores de la biblioteca son alcanzables con tu inventario actual y están cerca del objetivo.
      </p>
      <p class='mb-3 text-[11px] italic text-slate-400'>
        Sólo mostramos alternativas con ΔE ≤ 8 al objetivo — por encima, el cliente notaría un color claramente distinto y difícilmente lo aceptaría.
      </p>
      <div class='grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2' data-suggestions-alternativos></div>
    </div>

    {/* Empty state — shown when the reference library has nothing near */}
    <div class='mt-6 hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 text-xs text-slate-500' data-suggestions-empty>
      Aún no hay colores en la biblioteca de referencia cerca del objetivo. Agrégalos en <a href='/dashboard/references' class='font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:underline'>Colores de Referencia</a> para ver sugerencias aquí.
    </div>
  </Card>
</div>
